# pyinmean

<p align="center">
  <img alt="GitHub Actions Workflow Status" src="https://img.shields.io/github/actions/workflow/status/efraimdahl/pyinmean/main.yml?branch=release">
  <img alt="PyPI - Version" src="https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/pyinmean">
